a></p>\r\n[tt_spacer size=\"2.0em\"]\r\n<h3 class=\"text-center\">Experienced Professionals</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><!--row-->\r\n\r\n<p class=\"eqop\">We are an equal opportunity employer and are committed to the safety and welfare of our employees and clients.</p>','Grow your Career','','publish','open','open','','careers','','','2015-04-24 17:47:14','2015-04-24 17:47:14','',0,'http://ue.2020creative.org/?page_id=47',0,'page','',0),(49,1,'2015-01-23 19:29:41','2015-01-23 19:29:41','','Careers','','publish','open','open','','49','','','2015-04-28 14:11:55','2015-04-28 14:11:55','',0,'http://ue.2020creative.org/?p=49',11,'nav_menu_item','',0),(51,1,'2015-02-09 22:00:00','2015-02-09 22:00:00','United Excel Design (UED) provides a complete package of architectural and engineering services. The team specializes in healthcare planning, architectural design, interior design, structural engineering, mechanical engineering, electrical engineering, plumbing design, low voltage, communications, resource protection, way-finding, and graphic design. UED continually strives to develop sustainable, high-quality projects that meet clients’ design goals.\r\n<h2>Healthcare Expertise</h2>\r\n[PLACE HOSPITAL PHOTO(s)]\r\n\r\nWith a dedicated focus on being the highest quality healthcare design/builder in the industry, our family of companies is highly experienced in designing, managing, constructing and outfitting medical facilities. Since 1994, we have completed nearly 1,000 healthcare renovation, repair, addition and new construction projects.\r\n\r\nUEC, UED and Mill Creek employ a full staff of architects, engineers (including electrical, mechanical, plumbing, and structural), project managers, estimators, transition planners, initial outfitters and interior designers who continually stay apprised of cutting-edge health care industry and technical developments.\r\n\r\nOur portfolio of experience includes hospitals, ambulatory care facilities, research facilities, medical office buildings and senior living facilities as well as the installation and relocation of complex equipment, including MRIs, CTs, hybrid ORs and LASIK laser equipment.  Many of these projects occurred in fully operational facilities, requiring excellent transition support to minimize operational disruption.\r\n\r\nWith a proven track record of providing quality projects, on time and within budget, we can meet virtually any health care design need.','United Excel Design','','publish','open','open','','united-excel-design','','','2015-02-09 22:00:00','2015-02-09 22:00:00','',0,'http://ue.2020creative.org/?page_id=51',0,'page','',0),(53,1,'2015-02-09 22:11:09','2015-02-09 22:11:09','<h4>The IDBO family of companies works together to provide turnkey design-build-initial outfitting solutions. Our mission is to deliver profitable, quality, complex projects on schedule, on budget with complete customer satisfaction through caring, committed employees.</h4>\r\n\r\n[tt_posts cat_name=\"company\"]','Our Family of Companies','','publish','open','open','','about-us','','','2015-05-26 16:31:03','2015-05-26 16:31:03','',0,'http://ue.2020creative.org/?page_id=53',0,'page','',0),(55,1,'2015-02-09 22:12:36','2015-02-09 22:12:36','[tt_rule id=\"ue\"]\r\n\r\n<div class\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-offset-4 col-sm-4\">\r\n<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"http://ue.2020creative.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/logo-ue-300x89.png\" alt=\"logo-ue\"/>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n[tt_spacer size=\"2.0em\"]\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">  \r\nUnited Excel (UEC) is a performance-driven healthcare contractor committed to effectively managing and delivering successful projects on time and within budget.  UEC self-performs on-site supervision, quality control, safety, cost estimating, administration and management. The team is composed of project managers, administrators, superintendents and craftsmen who have built their careers on healthcare construction.\r\n<p class=\"text-center\">\r\n<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"http://www.unitedexcel.com\" target=\"_blank\"><i class=\"fa fa-external-link-square\"></i> View affiliate website</a></a>\r\n</div></div>\r\n\r\n[tt_rule id=\"mc\" top=\"y\"]  \r\n\r\n<div class\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-offset-3 col-sm-6\">\r\n<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"http://ue.2020creative.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/logo-millcreek.png\" alt=\"logo-mc\"/>\r\n</div></div>     \r\n[tt_spacer size=\"2.0em\"]\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\nMill Creek (MC) is a woman-owned small business that specializes in the outfitting of furniture, fixtures & equipment (FF&E), equipment planning, and transition/move management for commercial and healthcare facilities. The team offers project management solutions for budgeting, scheduling, procurement & installation and helps execute even the most complex transitions with minimal downtime.\r\n<p class=\"text-center\"><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"http://www.millcrk.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><i class=\"fa fa-external-link-square\"></i> View affiliate website</a></p>\r\n</div></div>\r\n\r\n[tt_rule id=\"ued\" top=\"y\"] \r\n\r\n<div class\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-offset-4 col-sm-4\">\r\n<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"http://ue.2020creative.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/logo-ued.png\" alt=\"logo-ue\"/>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>        \r\n[tt_spacer size=\"2.0em\"]\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\nUnited Excel Design (UED) provides a complete package of architectural design and engineering services. The team specializes in healthcare planning, architecture, structural engineering, mechanical engineering, electrical engineering, plumbing, interior design, way-finding, and graphic design. UED continually strives to develop sustainable, high-quality projects that meet clients’ design goals.\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-center\"><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"http://ued-stl.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><i class=\"fa fa-external-link-square\"></i> View affiliate website</a></p>\r\n</div></div>\r\n\r\n[tt_rule id=\"ued\" top=\"y\"] ','Affiliates','','trash','open','open','','affiliates','','','2015-04-28 14:31:19','2015-04-28 14:31:19','',0,'http://ue.2020creative.org/?page_id=55',0,'page','',0),(57,1,'2015-02-09 22:13:14','2015-02-09 22:13:14','','Portfolio','','publish','open','open','','portfolio','','','2015-03-20 21:55:36','2015-03-20 21:55:36','',0,'http://ue.2020creative.org/?page_id=57',0,'page','',0),(59,1,'2015-02-09 22:13:49','2015-02-09 22:13:49','[tt_section_row name=\"start\" note=\"-----------------Kansas City---------------------\"]\r\n[tt_section class=\"col-sm-4\"]\r\n<h2>Kansas City</h2>\r\n5425 Antioch Drive, Suite, 100</br>Merriam, KS 66202\r\n<h4>Ph. 913.647.9400</h4>\r\n<h5>Fax: 913.647.9500</h5>\r\n<a class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" href=\"#contact-form\">Contact us</a>\r\n[/tt_section]\r\n\r\n[tt_section class=\"location col-sm-8\"]\r\n<div class=\"city\">\r\n<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"http://ue.2020creative.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/kansas-city-skyline-400x400.jpg\" alt=\"Kansas City\" width=\"\" height=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"map\"><iframe style=\"border: 0;\" src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3099.35914865509!2d-94.687594!3d39.02992999999999!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x87c0ed0812bfc615%3A0xda1224ab264e64a0!2s5425+Antioch+Dr%2C+Mission%2C+KS+66202!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1426979268711\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></div>\r\n</div><!--map-->\r\n\r\n[/tt_section]\r\n[tt_section_row name=\"end\" note=\"--------------------------------------\"]\r\n\r\n[tt_rule]\r\n\r\n[tt_section_row name=\"start\" note=\"-------------St Louis-------------------------\"]\r\n[tt_section class=\"col-sm-4\"]\r\n<h2>St. Louis</h2>\r\n1807 Park 270 Drive, Suite 500</br>St. Louis, MO 63146\r\n<h4>Ph. 314.219.7940</h4>\r\n<h5>Fax: 314.218.3980</h5>\r\n<a class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\